This project incorporates code from the following projects:

1. Tiny386 (https://github.com/hchunhui/tiny386)
   Copyright (c) 2024-2025 Chunhui He
   i386 CPU emulator, peripheral emulation (PIC, PIT, VGA, etc.)
   License: BSD 3-Clause

2. Pico-286 (https://github.com/xrip/pico-286)
   Copyright (c) xrip
   RP2350 platform code, disk management, VGA driver concepts
   License: MIT

3. QuakeGeneric (https://github.com/DnCraptor/quakegeneric)
   Copyright (c) DnCraptor
   RP2350 hardware integration patterns
   License: GPL v2

4. SeaBIOS (https://www.seabios.org/)
   Copyright (c) Kevin O'Connor and contributors
   x86 BIOS and VGA BIOS firmware
   License: GNU LGPL v3

5. FatFs (http://elm-chan.org/fsw/ff/)
   Copyright (c) ChaN
   Generic FAT Filesystem Module for SD card access
   License: FatFs License (BSD-style)

6. Pico SDK (https://github.com/raspberrypi/pico-sdk)
   Copyright (c) 2020-2024 Raspberry Pi (Trading) Ltd.
   RP2350 SDK and libraries
